osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e6f8d5ea4b876766a0f876460ca83cb3d1301","tid":335344,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦數啦 又未拎banner大叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印好曬banner未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dece0f686ecb140f2f5864ebd69435b1d6d29eff","tid":335344,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/10_pro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F10_pro.jpg&h=dfd51203&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梁國雄說，未有強行進入會議室，是不想傷害保安的身體，與他們一直以來不傷害人命、財產的抗爭手段相符，「我哋唔入去，唔係代表我哋怯懦；我哋唔入去，係表達咗我哋對於我哋同事嘅珍重，佢哋係人肉盾，我哋冇辦法穿過。」<br />\n<br />\n原本長毛就以一敵百既，可惜佢唔想傷害其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84a426eda7137b1e35fbd04ab174bec9bd6f54c","tid":335344,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算啦數啦 又未拎banner大叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印好曬banner未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ne-print股價上升"},{"pid":"7ddc99102aaaa727a61e6b89bcdbe14773a8bfd6","tid":335344,"uid":34927,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/10_pro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F10_pro.jpg&h=dfd51203&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梁國雄說，未有強行進入會議室，是不想傷害保安的身體，與他們一直以來不傷害人命、財產的抗爭手段相符，「我哋唔入去，唔係代表我哋怯懦；我哋唔入去，係表達咗我哋對於我哋同事嘅珍重，佢哋係人肉盾，我哋冇辦法穿過。」<br />\n<br />\n原本長毛就以一敵百既，可惜佢唔想傷害其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如長毛唔好呼吸分薄其他人既空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97a190ef5e43896291a411bc823f4c551922037","tid":335344,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/10_pro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F10_pro.jpg&h=dfd51203&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n漏咗限時絕食"},{"pid":"082ff0098a6411a6047c75bf7a663efd64d39084","tid":335344,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁上面班垃圾又做過啲乜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年某狗唔係話搞地盤嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓咗冇睇，其實搞咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497a68ae1e016effd07fad10efa0d8b4fc5ab238","tid":335344,"uid":116443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:42:34.000Z","msg":"有時真係覺得投白鴿黨不如索性投民建聯，人地光明正大做擦鞋仔，你班友就唔適當嘅時候係度搞搞震，真係要你反嘅時候就係度玩妥協，冇撚用"},{"pid":"ebaa301caf1146bbced99ce1b5a3f44ed31945d5","tid":335344,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"ab5948edfea500092c6a9e7e4b0f466088ac4b6a","tid":335344,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"好文重溫 <br />\n<br />\n劉慧卿曾評估，認為高鐵項目可望於昨日財委會加開三節會議期間表決、也無意把會議再延長，但由於泛民主派議員的拉布策略，會議昨日的財委會還是需延至傍晚六時半才能正式進行表決。泛民與建制派高鐵撥款存在嚴重分歧，身為泛民主派的主席劉慧卿左右做人難，當她決定縮短發問時間至兩分鐘時，引起泛民強烈反彈，其黨友何俊仁及公民黨部分議員均作出嚴厲批評，直斥其決定會適得其反。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然她成功縮短發言時間，但因亦未有嚴格執行時間管理，不少議員發問逾時未作阻止、也不制止部分議員再三就一地兩檢及諮詢不足等範疇提問，結果又招來建制派反彈，要求她嚴格執行主席職權。 <br />\n<br />\n成功通過高鐵撥款後，社民連隨即要求繼續討論財委會餘下其他議程包括興建北大嶼山醫院等項目，但劉慧卿指已與政府達成共識，昨日的會議就此結束，再惹來陳偉業強烈批評。 <br />\n<br />\n劉慧卿於會後表示，對於議員的批評感到「無所謂」，認為是議員的自由；又指批評者應指出她究竟違反哪項議事規則，強調公道自在人心。建制派的劉秀成表示欣賞她的表現，指她可顧全大局。"},{"pid":"3dbf1e3a9a18b6582882ef260bf285cbd3303699","tid":335344,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"靠班泛民係無用"},{"pid":"b317e235b3b209dfafd9df8f3dc3b4c821e9c54c","tid":335344,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"一班狗官<br />\n我屌"},{"pid":"9d9cef9c8044f65da531805ed09b057f8c16e983","tid":335344,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"嘩，咁犀利呀？"},{"pid":"f8f96e776e00aba310ed23fafdf2c4be8d5669b6","tid":335344,"uid":8478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"靠泛民不如靠三登仔鍵盤抗爭<br />\n可能勝算仲大過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632151df423158f3a6f544fcfb71ebc205d048b0","tid":335344,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"成日話泛民無用,其實我地咪一樣無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebcf9ebeacb60982263d8aa56b524bd1d175ecf","tid":335344,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,